months) was significantly shorter than in the PC-DCM-AF group (21.9 months) or 
PC-DCM-SR group (29.1 months, P=0.001). CHF-DCM-AF in IW was associated with 
reduced life expectancy and CD, while most IW with preclinical DCM died from 
non-cardiac causes.

