Current knowledge in pathophysiology and management of Budd-Chiari syndrome and 
non-cirrhotic non-tumoral splanchnic vein thrombosis.

Hernández-Gea V(1), De Gottardi A(2), Leebeek FWG(3), Rautou PE(4), Salem R(5), 
